Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.19,0:00:06.37,Default,en,0,0,0,,It is the turbulent Sengoku period.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.67,0:00:11.14,Default,en,0,0,0,,Warlords keep on fighting day and night over\NJipangu State, where Karakuri people live.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.65,0:00:16.13,Default,en,0,0,0,,Karakuri martial artists were sharpening their swords, dreaming of victory and honor.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.65,0:00:23.01,Default,en,0,0,0,,And now, a wild hero has arrived, seeking to be the number one Karakuri martial artist!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.24,0:00:26.73,Default,en,0,0,0,,Musashi is here-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
